"Your Cutling keyboard is ready! While typing anywhere, tap the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to switch to Cutling." = "Kibodi yako ya Cutling iko tayari! Unapoandika popote, gusa ikoni ya 🌐 ulimwengu kwenye kibodi yako ili kubadili hadi Cutling.";
