/* MARK: - Interactive Tutorial (iOS walkthrough) */
"How to Use Cutling" = "Jinsi ya Kutumia Cutling";
"Create a cutling" = "Tengeneza cutling";
"Tap + to save text or an image you reuse often." = "Gusa + ili kuhifadhi maandishi au picha unayotumia mara kwa mara.";
"Edit a cutling" = "Hariri cutling";
"Touch and hold any card, then choose Edit to change it." = "Gusa na ushikilie kadi yoyote, kisha uchague Hariri ili kuibadilisha.";
"Delete a cutling" = "Futa cutling";
"Touch and hold a card, then choose Delete to remove it." = "Gusa na ushikilie kadi, kisha uchague Futa ili kuiondoa.";
"Recover a cutling" = "Rejesha cutling";
"Open the More menu, then Recently Deleted, to restore anything you removed." = "Fungua menyu ya Chaguzi zaidi, kisha Iliyofutwa hivi karibuni, ili kurejesha chochote ulichoondoa.";
"Touch and hold a deleted cutling, then tap Recover." = "Gusa na ushikilie cutling iliyofutwa, kisha ugusa Rejesha.";
"Recovered! Your cutling is back." = "Imerejeshwa! Cutling yako imerudi.";
"Tap + to start a new text cutling." = "Gusa + ili kuanza cutling mpya ya maandishi.";
"Give your cutling a name." = "Ipe cutling yako jina.";
"Now type the text you want to save." = "Sasa andika maandishi unayotaka kuhifadhi.";
"Tap here to save your cutling." = "Gusa hapa ili kuhifadhi cutling yako.";
"Edit the text, then tap here to save." = "Hariri maandishi, kisha ugusa hapa ili kuhifadhi.";
"Edit the text, then tap Back. Your changes save automatically." = "Hariri maandishi, kisha ugusa Rudi. Mabadiliko yako huhifadhiwa kiotomatiki.";
"Edit anything, then go back to save." = "Hariri chochote, kisha rudi nyuma ili kuhifadhi.";
"Edit the text or anything else you like." = "Hariri maandishi au kitu kingine chochote unachopenda.";
"Tap a deleted cutling to bring it back." = "Gusa cutling iliyofutwa ili kuirejesha.";
"Nice! Your cutling is saved." = "Vyema! Cutling yako imehifadhiwa.";
"Tap the ⋯ button on a card to open and edit it." = "Gusa kitufe cha ⋯ kwenye kadi ili kuifungua na kuihariri.";
"To delete, open a cutling with the ⋯ button." = "Ili kufuta, fungua cutling kwa kitufe cha ⋯.";
"Scroll down and tap Delete Cutling to remove it." = "Sogeza chini na ugusa Futa Cutling ili kuiondoa.";
"Skip Tutorial" = "Ruka Mafunzo";

/* MARK: - TipKit */
"Saved cutlings" = "Cutling zilizohifadhiwa";
"Your pinned snippets live here, ready to copy with one click." = "Vipande vyako vilivyobandikwa vinaishi hapa, vikiwa tayari kunakiliwa kwa mbofyo mmoja.";
"Recent clipboard" = "Ubao wa kunakili wa hivi karibuni";
"Everything you copy lands here. Right-click any row to save it as a cutling." = "Kila kitu unachonakili huingia hapa. Bonyeza-kulia kwenye safu yoyote ili kuihifadhi kama Cutling.";
"Wipe the list" = "Futa orodha";
"Empties your recent clipboard. Saved cutlings stay put." = "Hufuta ubao wako wa kunakili wa hivi karibuni. Cutling zilizohifadhiwa zinabaki.";
"Rebind the hotkey, toggle clipboard capture, and manage iCloud sync." = "Weka upya kitufe cha mkato, washa/zima kunasa ubao wa kunakili, na simamia usawazishaji wa iCloud.";
"Undo deletes" = "Tendua ufutaji";
"Deleted cutlings stay here for 30 days. Restore them or empty for good." = "Cutling zilizofutwa zinabaki hapa kwa siku 30. Zirejeshe au futa kabisa.";
"Tap here to select multiple cutlings, reorder them, or restore recently deleted ones." = "Gusa hapa kuchagua Cutling nyingi, kuzipanga upya, au kurejesha zile zilizofutwa hivi karibuni.";
"Long-press a cutling" = "Bonyeza kwa muda mrefu kwenye Cutling";
"Hold any card for quick actions: copy, edit, share, or delete." = "Shikilia kadi yoyote kwa vitendo vya haraka: nakili, hariri, shiriki, au futa.";
"Drag to select" = "Buruta ili kuchagua";
"Swipe across cards to select a range. Swipe back over them to deselect." = "Telezesha kwenye kadi ili kuchagua safu. Telezesha kurudi ili kuondoa chaguo.";
"Smart field matching" = "Ulinganishaji wa uwanja mahiri";
"Cutling spots email, URL, phone, and address fields, then floats matching snippets to the top of the keyboard." = "Cutling hutambua sehemu za barua pepe, URL, simu na anwani, na kuinua vipande vinavyolingana juu ya kibodi.";
"Create a new cutling" = "Tengeneza Cutling mpya";
"Save text or image snippets you'll reuse from any app." = "Hifadhi vipande vya maandishi au picha ambavyo utavitumia tena kutoka programu yoyote.";

/* MARK: - Welcome Window (macOS first launch) */
"Welcome to Cutling" = "Karibu kwenye Cutling";
"Your clipboard, organised." = "Ubao wako wa kunakili, umepangwa vizuri.";
"Save the snippets, images, and links you reuse. Capture everything you copy. Paste anywhere with one shortcut." = "Hifadhi vipande, picha na viungo unavyotumia tena. Nasa kila kitu unachonakili. Bandika popote kwa njia ya mkato moja.";
"Look up. Cutling lives in your menu bar" = "Angalia juu. Cutling iko kwenye upau wa menyu";
"The clipboard icon at the top of your screen opens Cutling any time. Click it to see your saved cutlings and recent clipboard history." = "Ikoni ya ubao wa kunakili juu ya skrini yako hufungua Cutling wakati wowote. Bofya ili kuona cutlings zilizohifadhiwa na historia ya ubao wa kunakili ya hivi karibuni.";
"Summon Cutling from anywhere" = "Ita Cutling kutoka popote";
"Press ⌘⇧V from any app to open a floating picker at your cursor. Pick a cutling and it's ready to paste, no menu bar trip required." = "Bonyeza ⌘⇧V kutoka programu yoyote ili kufungua kichagua kinachoelea kwenye mshale wako. Chagua cutling na uko tayari kubandika, bila kuhitaji kwenda kwenye upau wa menyu.";
"Rebind it later in Settings → Hotkey." = "Unaweza kubadilisha baadaye katika Mipangilio → Kibodi ya Mkato.";
"Almost there" = "Karibu kufika";
"You're all set" = "Uko tayari kabisa";
"Two quick permissions so Cutling can work the way you'd expect. You can change either later in Settings." = "Ruhusa mbili za haraka ili Cutling ifanye kazi kama unavyotarajia. Unaweza kubadilisha yoyote baadaye katika Mipangilio.";
"Launch at login" = "Anzisha unapoingia";
"Open Cutling automatically when you sign in." = "Fungua Cutling kiotomatiki unapoingia.";
"Accessibility access" = "Ufikiaji wa Ufikivu";
"Granted. Cutling can paste directly into other apps." = "Imeruhusiwa. Cutling inaweza kubandika moja kwa moja kwenye programu nyingine.";
"Lets Cutling paste a cutling straight into the app you were using." = "Inaruhusu Cutling kubandika cutling moja kwa moja kwenye programu uliyokuwa unaitumia.";
"Grant" = "Ruhusu";
"You can skip Accessibility and grant it later from Settings → Paste." = "Unaweza kuruka Ufikivu na uiruhusu baadaye kutoka Mipangilio → Bandika.";


/* MARK: - Image Saving (macOS) */
"Save as File…" = "Hifadhi kama faili…";
"Image Saving" = "Uhifadhi wa picha";
"When saving images" = "Wakati wa kuhifadhi picha";
"Ask each time" = "Uliza kila wakati";
"Save to folder" = "Hifadhi kwenye folda";
"Folder" = "Folda";
"Change Folder…" = "Badilisha folda…";
"Choose how the “Save as File” action works for image cutlings. With “Save to folder”, images go straight into the folder you pick with a unique filename, no prompt." = "Chagua jinsi kitendo cha “Hifadhi kama faili” kinavyofanya kazi kwa Cutling za picha. Ukichagua “Hifadhi kwenye folda”, picha huhifadhiwa moja kwa moja kwenye folda uliyochagua kwa jina la faili la kipekee, bila kuuliza.";
"Choose" = "Chagua";
"Choose Image Folder" = "Chagua folda ya picha";
"Pick a folder where Cutling will save image cutlings." = "Chagua folda ambapo Cutling itahifadhi Cutling za picha.";
"Preview" = "Onyesho la awali";


/* MARK: - Newly added keys */
"Saved" = "Zilizohifadhiwa";
"History" = "Historia";
"No saved cutlings yet" = "Bado hakuna Cutling zilizohifadhiwa";
"Copy something to see it here" = "Nakili kitu ili kuona hapa";
"Clipboard history is off. Enable it in Settings." = "Historia ya ubao wa kunakili imezimwa. Iwashe katika Mipangilio.";
"Spotlight" = "Spotlight";
"Include in Spotlight Search" = "Jumuisha katika utafutaji wa Spotlight";
"Make your cutlings searchable from Spotlight. Sensitive content (credit cards, API keys, JWT tokens, seed phrases, private keys) is never indexed." = "Fanya Cutling zako zitafutwa kupitia Spotlight. Maudhui nyeti (kadi za mkopo, funguo za API, tokeni za JWT, vifungu vya seed, funguo za faragha) hayaorodheshwi kamwe.";
"Copy Cutling" = "Nakili Cutling";
"Copy a cutling's contents to the clipboard." = "Hunakili maudhui ya Cutling kwenye ubao wa kunakili.";
"Use these phrases with Siri or browse all Cutling shortcuts in the Shortcuts app." = "Tumia misemo hii pamoja na Siri au vinjari njia za mkato za Cutling zote katika programu ya Njia za Mkato.";
"Copied \"%@\"" = "“%@” imenakiliwa";

/* MARK: - Paste Settings (macOS) - Direct Paste opt-in */
"Paste directly into other apps" = "Bandika moja kwa moja kwenye programu zingine";
"When on, picking a cutling from the hotkey-summoned picker sends a single ⌘V keystroke into the app that was frontmost, so the cutling is pasted at the cursor. Off by default. When off, Cutling copies to the clipboard and you paste manually with ⌘V." = "Ikiwa imewashwa, kuchagua Cutling kutoka kichagua kinachofunguliwa kwa funguo ya mkato hutuma mbofyo mmoja wa ⌘V kwa programu iliyokuwa mbele, hivyo Cutling inabandikwa kwenye kishale. Imezimwa kwa chaguo-msingi. Ikiwa imezimwa, Cutling inanakili kwenye ubao wa kunakili na unabandika kwa mkono kwa kutumia ⌘V.";
"Permission" = "Ruhusa";
"Cutling uses Accessibility access only to send the ⌘V keystroke to the previously focused app after you pick a cutling. It does not read other apps' UI or control your computer." = "Cutling hutumia Ufikiaji wa Ufikivu pekee kutuma mbofyo wa ⌘V kwa programu iliyokuwa imelenga awali baada ya kuchagua Cutling. Haisomi UI ya programu zingine au kudhibiti kompyuta yako.";
"Direct Paste" = "Bandika Moja kwa Moja";
"Direct paste needs Accessibility access." = "Bandika moja kwa moja kunahitaji Ufikiaji wa Ufikivu.";

/* MARK: - Updates (macOS, direct-download build) */
"Updates" = "Masasisho";
"Check for Updates…" = "Angalia Masasisho…";
"Check for updates automatically" = "Angalia masasisho kiotomatiki";
"Cutling can update itself to new versions. Turn on automatic checks, or check for updates manually any time." = "Cutling inaweza kujisasisha yenyewe hadi matoleo mapya. Washa ukaguzi wa kiotomatiki, au angalia masasisho kwa mkono wakati wowote.";
"Automatic updates" = "Masasisho ya kiotomatiki";
"Let Cutling check for and install new versions on its own." = "Ruhusu Cutling iangalie na kusakinisha matoleo mapya yenyewe.";
"A few quick settings so Cutling can work the way you'd expect. You can change any of these later in Settings." = "Mipangilio michache ya haraka ili Cutling ifanye kazi kama unavyotarajia. Unaweza kubadilisha yoyote kati ya haya baadaye katika Mipangilio.";
